    "description": "Navigate a local princess through the pages of a hand-crafted fairy tale and help her solve the mystery of a golden ring in this narrative-driven point-and-click adventure game with multiple endings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/221325aeae4e0ca508611f51f753fc96.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>Yup, it’s a short game. It will only take you about 15 minutes to complete it. Well, maybe 30 minutes if you are a real achievement hunter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/d379f3653cc5e76efa7a4601e1440b03.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>Every action (and inaction) has its consequences. Every decision can lead to catastrophic results. Like whether you decide to dig up a skeleton in a peaceful forest clearing or let it rest. Or cross a rickety bridge over a deep ravine. Or… well, you’ll discover the rest yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/d41e5a6012087767d347e713a8c9f344.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>This game has five endings. Sad, epic, controversial… Some are happier than others. Will you dare to unlock all of them?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/e1e61da95b5046734c35505d372615a1.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>Like any self-respecting fairy tale, this story has a charismatic narrator, an adventurous hero, and a couple of mysterious strangers. All of them have voices - literally and metaphorically. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/b0f294bd4058f02a0535a8888d172913.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>This game is crafted in full 2D. Like back in the day, when the grass was greener and the third dimension was a subject of legends and myths. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321970/extras/7ffbd46c3b2d34232e1b4e11d6cad511.webp?t=1704739428\" width=622 height=45 /></span><br><br>Just come on in and play. There is no microtransactions, NFTs, paywalls, or other greedy creatures.<br><br>Enjoy the journey!",
